name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
There are still many students who submit articles to me, hoping that I will expose the fact that their schools are about to start.
My opinion is that it is not very useful for you to send me articles. Now all middle schools in the country are starting school, and you are not an exception.
I think if you are really afraid, you can communicate with your parents and ask them to help you take leave. I believe that if your parents are concerned about your health, they will take the initiative to help you do so.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: You submit articles to me because you are afraid that you will be punished if you don't go to school, so the best way is to ask me to close the school directly, but the school can't be scared to open the school because of my tweet. You still have to face what you have to face. If you think your life is more important than punishment, then you can just stay at home and not go to school. At most, you will repeat a year. You don't need to rely on external forces.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
You should communicate more with the parents, or ask the parents to communicate with the school. I really can't help you with anything.
That's all.
